Nancy Dussault https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Nancy_Dussault 0 Nancy Dussault (born June 30, 1936) is an American actress and singer. She is best known for her role in the sitcom Too Close for Comfort (1980–1987). In a career spanning over half a century, Dussault received two Tony Award nominations.
